title: Yulia Tymoshenko | Biography & Facts | Britannica
snippet: Yulia Tymoshenko (born November 27, 1960, Dnipropetrovsk, Ukraine, U.S.S.R. [now in Ukraine]) is a Ukrainian businesswoman and politician who served as prime minister of Ukraine (2005, 2007–10).
